    "sourceText": "1880"
  },
  {
    "id": "george-eastman.timeline.2.event",
    "sourceText": "미국 특허 226,503 'Method and Apparatus for Coating Plates' 발행 (4월)"
  },
  {
    "id": "george-eastman.timeline.3.year",
